# CSS rules (SVG-safe)

## Scoping
- Every selector MUST be under `#svg-main ...` to avoid leaking into host pages.

## Naming
- Utility classes: `text-<style>-*`, `bg-<style>-*`, `image-*`
- Plugin-specific classes: `<plugin>-*` (avoid generic names like `.title`)

## Prefer
- CSS variables over hard-coded colors
- small reusable utilities over large custom blocks

## Avoid
- global selectors without `#svg-main`
- `!important` unless absolutely necessary
